  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the Queen of Mountain and Vale, see <a href=\"/index.php/Teora_Hunter\" title=\"Teora Hunter\">Teora Hunter</a>. For the Lady of Casterly Rock, see <a href=\"/index.php/Teora_Kyndall\" title=\"Teora Kyndall\">Teora Kyndall</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Toland\" title=\"House Toland\"><img alt=\"House Toland.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/House_Toland.svg/50px-House_Toland.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/House_Toland.svg/75px-House_Toland.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f1/House_Toland.svg/100px-House_Toland.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Teora Toland</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Toland\" title=\"House Toland\"><img alt=\"House Toland.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/House_Toland.svg/50px-House_Toland.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f1/House_Toland.svg/75px-House_Toland.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f1/House_Toland.svg/100px-House_Toland.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Teora_Toland_by_askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Teora Toland by askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/00/Teora_Toland_by_askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg/350px-Teora_Toland_by_askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/00/Teora_Toland_by_askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg/525px-Teora_Toland_by_askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/00/Teora_Toland_by_askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg/700px-Teora_Toland_by_askmeaboutmyoctopustheory.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Teora Toland, by askmeaboutmyoctopustheory ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Toland\" title=\"House Toland\">House Toland</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dornish\">Dornish</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Nymella_Toland\" title=\"Nymella Toland\">Nymella Toland</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Teora Toland</b> is the younger daughter of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Nymella_Toland\" title=\"Nymella Toland\">Nymella Toland</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost_Hill\" title=\"Ghost Hill\">Ghost Hill</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teora_Toland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Teora, unlike her sister <a href=\"/index.php/Valena_Toland\" title=\"Valena Toland\">Valena</a>, is short, plump, and shy. The only trait they share is their red hair. Teora seems to have <a href=\"/index.php/Dreams_and_prophecies\" title=\"Dreams and prophecies\">prophetic dreams</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teora_Toland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Teora dislikes Ghost Hill's <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">maester</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Toman\" title=\"Toman\">Toman</a>, due to the fact that he dismisses her dreams and attributes them to her adolescence and eating sweet <a href=\"/index.php/Food\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Food\">foods</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teora_Toland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teora_Toland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a> and her companions arrive at <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost_Hill\" title=\"Ghost Hill\">Ghost Hill</a>, Teora is present at the welcome feast where Arianne and Lady Nymella discuss the possible threat of the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>'s invasion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a>. When Arianne says they have yet to determine whether they are friends or foes, Teora finally looks up from her plate and states they are <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>. Her mother dismisses this as madness, but Teora insists that dragons are coming. Valena scornfully asks if she learned that from her \"little dreams\", and Teora tremblingly replies that the dragons were dancing in her dream, and everywhere they danced people died. Lady Nymella exasperatedly blames Teora's dreams on eating too many creamcakes during puberty, as Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Toman\" title=\"Toman\">Toman</a> has said. Teora says that she hates the maester, and flees from the table, leaving her mother to apologize for her.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teora_Toland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Teora:</b> It is <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a>.<br />\n</p><p><b>Nymella:</b> Dragons? Teora, don't be mad.<br />\n<b>Teora:</b> I'm not. They're coming.<br />\n<b>Valena:</b> How could you possibly know that? One of your little <a href=\"/index.php/Dreams\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dreams\">dreams</a>?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Teora:</b> They were dancing. In my dream. And everywhere the dragons danced the people died.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Teora, <a href=\"/index.php/Nymella_Toland\" title=\"Nymella Toland\">Nymella</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Valena_Toland\" title=\"Valena Toland\">Valena Toland</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Nymella:</b> If you did not eat so many creamcakes you would not have such dreams. Rich foods are not for girls your age, when your humors are so unbalanced. <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Toman\" title=\"Toman\">Toman</a> says&#8212;<br />\n<b>Teora:</b> I <i>hate</i> Maester Toman.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Barianne_i_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Carianne_i.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Nymella_Toland\" title=\"Nymella Toland\">Nymella</a> and Teora Toland</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teora_Toland&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Nymella_Toland\" title=\"Nymella Toland\">Nymella</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />husband</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"borde